headline: Raymond James Raises Devon Energy (DVN) PT to $46 From $45
summary: Devon Energy Corporation (NYSE:DVN) is one of the S&P 500 stocks with a low PE ratio. Devon Energy, an independent Oklahoma-based energy firm, is involved in the exploration, development, and production of oil, natural gas, and natural gas liquids.
